<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss version="2.0"><channel><title>每日重点简报</title><link>https://youngwilly.github.io/chatgpt-task-rss</link><description>ChatGPT 计划任务原文订阅</description><language>zh-cn</language><item><title>每日重点简报</title><link>https://youngwilly.github.io/chatgpt-task-rss/daily-brief.html#daily-brief-2026-07-13T15-51-18Z</link><guid isPermaLink="false">bd0f1def53d9a9a2d7c8ac6ccfd9d48e6f89fbfe8808aac445ee7b1a7a645993</guid><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 15:51:18 GMT</pubDate><description><![CDATA[<div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><h1 data-section-id="1ry2jbx" data-start="0" data-end="10">每日重点简报</h1>
<p data-start="11" data-end="21">2026年7月13日</p>
<h2 data-section-id="1f5t9tx" data-start="23" data-end="37">1. 昨夜美股收盘概览</h2>
<p data-start="39" data-end="212">美国周末没有新收盘，周五留下来的价格仍是今天亚洲盘的起点。SPY收754.95美元，涨0.39%；QQQ收725.51美元，涨0.28%；DIA收525.78美元，涨0.31%。Nvidia涨4.02%至210.96美元，AMD涨2.06%至557.89美元，Apple跌0.29%至315.32美元，Micron跌1.30%至979.30美元。</p>
<p data-start="214" data-end="366">周五那场还能继续看出资金偏好。Nvidia单日成交约1.48亿股，市值超过5.1万亿美元，市场继续往算力龙头集中。Micron盘中从955美元拉到接近998美元，最后仍收跌，存储线的分歧没有消失。AMD市盈率接近183倍，远高于Nvidia约32倍，后面一旦AI订单增速低于预期，AMD的估值波动会更大。</p>
<h2 data-section-id="1dja103" data-start="368" data-end="379">2. 宏观与政策</h2>
<p data-start="381" data-end="538">今天早上真正改变盘面的东西来自中东。美国和伊朗周末继续互相发动导弹及无人机打击，伊朗宣布关闭霍尔木兹海峡，美国则称航道仍保持开放。Reuters报道，Brent周一亚洲盘上涨3.51%至78.68美元，WTI上涨3.47%至73.89美元。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 77px;"><a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/iran-declares-strait-hormuz-closed-unauthorised-vessel-hit-2026-07-11/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" alt="https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/iran-declares-strait-hormuz-closed-unauthorised-vessel-hit-2026-07-11/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 77px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.reuters.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Reuters</span></span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+1</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<p data-start="540" data-end="702">政治表态现在有冲突，船到底能不能顺利走过去更重要。AP称，过去一周仍有超过140艘船通过，但周末一艘塞浦路斯旗集装箱船遇袭起火，一名船员失踪，美国随后扩大对伊朗的空袭。运输量如果继续下降，油价会先过80美元，随后影响美债收益率、航空、化工和消费预期。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 68px;"><a href="https://apnews.com/article/0764d17c09370a8c5cf1e8197a8878ab?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" alt="https://apnews.com/article/0764d17c09370a8c5cf1e8197a8878ab?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 68px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://apnews.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">AP News</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<p data-start="704" data-end="849">本周美国CPI、PPI、零售销售连续公布。Reuters称，投资者会用CPI重新调整利率预期，美股二季度财报季也同时启动。现在油价在数据公布前先跳了一次，通胀数据即使符合预期，市场也会开始往7月能源成本上升的方向算。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 63px;"><a href="https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/wall-st-week-ahead-investors-grapple-with-packed-week-earnings-cpi-iran-2026-07-10/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" alt="https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/wall-st-week-ahead-investors-grapple-with-packed-week-earnings-cpi-iran-2026-07-10/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 63px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.reuters.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Reuters</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<h2 data-section-id="pskzhu" data-start="851" data-end="864">3. AI与科技产业</h2>
<p data-start="866" data-end="1028">Meta计划从9月开始生产自研AI芯片，同时把明年总算力提高到14吉瓦。这个动作比单纯买GPU更值得留意。Meta一边买Nvidia，一边做内部芯片，一边研究把富余算力卖给外部客户，目的很直接，降低推理成本，把巨额资本开支变成可计算的收入和成本节约。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 63px;"><a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/meta-put-ai-chip-into-production-september-it-looks-double-computing-capacity-2026-07-09/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" alt="https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/meta-put-ai-chip-into-production-september-it-looks-double-computing-capacity-2026-07-09/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 63px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.reuters.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Reuters</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<p data-start="1030" data-end="1212">SK海力士CEO预计，2027年可能出现史上最严重的内存短缺，需求将持续超过供应。UBS预计全球DRAM供应紧张可能延续到2028年二季度。这个说法给Micron、SK海力士和HBM设备链提供支撑，不过市场已经在提前交易巨额扩产，后面只看缺货口号不够，新增产能、客户预付款和长期合同更有用。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 63px;"><a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sk-hynix-ceo-sees-worst-ever-memory-supply-shortage-2027-says-demand-outstrip-2026-07-10/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" alt="https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sk-hynix-ceo-sees-worst-ever-memory-supply-shortage-2027-says-demand-outstrip-2026-07-10/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 63px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.reuters.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Reuters</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<p data-start="1214" data-end="1354">本周TSMC、ASML都要公布业绩。AI芯片订单会经过TSMC晶圆代工、CoWoS封装和ASML设备三层验证。只要TSMC继续上调先进制程和封装需求，Nvidia、Broadcom、AMD及半导体设备还能维持强势。资本开支增速明显超过订单增速，市场会马上讨论2027年产能利用率。</p>
<h2 data-section-id="f3wogl" data-start="1356" data-end="1368">4. 全球重大新闻</h2>
<p data-start="1370" data-end="1497">美国和伊朗周末的攻击范围已经扩大到海湾多个国家。Reuters称，伊朗打击了驻有美军设施的海湾国家，美国周日下午又启动新一轮对伊打击。外交谈判还在，但军事行动的频率和范围都上来了。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 63px;"><a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/iran-declares-strait-hormuz-closed-unauthorised-vessel-hit-2026-07-11/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" alt="https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/iran-declares-strait-hormuz-closed-unauthorised-vessel-hit-2026-07-11/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 63px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.reuters.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Reuters</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<p data-start="1499" data-end="1642">IEA此前警告，美伊冲突可能破坏原本预计在2027年出现的石油供应过剩。油价眼下仍低于今年战争高点，成品油和炼化环节已经更紧。原油涨3%，柴油、航空燃油和运费可能涨得更快，这个地方会直接压航空、物流和制造业利润。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 77px;"><a href="https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-iran-escalation-could-threaten-2027-oil-market-surplus-iea-says-2026-07-10/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" alt="https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-iran-escalation-could-threaten-2027-oil-market-surplus-iea-says-2026-07-10/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 77px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.reuters.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Reuters</span></span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+1</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<h2 data-section-id="njlh0x" data-start="1644" data-end="1657">5. 中国市场与政策</h2>
<p data-start="1659" data-end="1811">中国资产近期和全球市场走出了点不同的节奏。Reuters称，人民币、中国债券及部分股票与全球科技股、美债的相关性下降，海外投资者开始增加分散配置。这个变化还不算大，至少在美伊冲突和美股估值偏高的时候，中国资产有了一点独立交易逻辑。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 63px;"><a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-breaks-step-with-global-markets-investors-buy-2026-07-07/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" alt="https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-breaks-step-with-global-markets-investors-buy-2026-07-07/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 63px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.reuters.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Reuters</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<p data-start="1813" data-end="1956">国内经济仍是高科技制造相对强，消费和地产偏弱。5月零售销售出现三年多来首次同比下降，投资也偏软，工业生产更多依靠出口和制造业支撑。国产芯片、机器人、AI服务器可以继续活跃，大盘消费和传统顺周期未必跟着一起走。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 63px;"><a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-may-retail-sales-fall-first-time-over-three-years-2026-06-16/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" alt="https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-may-retail-sales-fall-first-time-over-three-years-2026-06-16/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 63px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.reuters.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Reuters</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<p data-start="1958" data-end="2092">IMF已把2026年全球增长预测小幅下调至3.0%，理由包括中东战争、贸易碎片化和AI资产预期可能修正。对中国出口链来说，AI服务器和高端制造还有需求，普通制造、低利润出口和欧洲业务会更难。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 63px;"><a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/china/imf-edges-2026-global-growth-forecast-lower-3-sees-rebound-2027-2026-07-08/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" alt="https://www.reuters.com/world/china/imf-edges-2026-global-growth-forecast-lower-3-sees-rebound-2027-2026-07-08/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 63px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.reuters.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Reuters</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<h2 data-section-id="1e14sqf" data-start="2094" data-end="2109">6. 公司重大事件与财报</h2>
<p data-start="2111" data-end="2261">JPMorgan和Goldman Sachs将在7月14日公布二季度业绩。JPMorgan约在美东时间上午7点发布数据，8点30分召开电话会；Goldman同日发布。市场会盯交易收入、投行业务、净息差、贷款增长和信用损失。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 117px;"><a href="https://www.jpmorganchase.com/ir/news/2026/jpmc-to-host-second-quarter-2026-earnings-call?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" alt="https://www.jpmorganchase.com/ir/news/2026/jpmc-to-host-second-quarter-2026-earnings-call?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 117px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.jpmorganchase.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">JPMorgan Chase</span></span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+1</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<p data-start="2263" data-end="2415">Reuters统计，市场预计标普500公司二季度盈利同比增长约24%，科技仍是主要贡献。这个预期已经很高。银行财报如果只小幅超预期，股价未必会买账。市场活跃度上升能推高交易和投行收入，消费者信用、商业地产和贷款需求可能拖后腿。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 63px;"><a href="https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/sp-500-nasdaq-futures-slip-investors-eye-sk-hynix-listing-middle-east-risks-2026-07-10/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" alt="https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/sp-500-nasdaq-futures-slip-investors-eye-sk-hynix-listing-middle-east-risks-2026-07-10/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 63px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.reuters.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Reuters</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<h2 data-section-id="68814y" data-start="2417" data-end="2429">7. 今日投资机会</h2>
<p data-start="2431" data-end="2511">油价已经先涨3%以上，能源和油服会直接受益。开盘后要看Brent能不能站稳78美元，继续向80美元走，能源股还有延续性；很快回落到76美元附近，追高会比较难受。</p>
<p data-start="2513" data-end="2609">AI链条仍然偏强，资金会更挑。Nvidia趋势最好，210美元上方的赔率已经没前面舒服。TSMC、ASML、先进封装、光模块、服务器电源和数据中心电力，本周有财报或订单验证，位置相对更容易找。</p>
<p data-start="2611" data-end="2709">银行股适合看财报后的分化。JPMorgan和Goldman受益于交易、IPO和并购恢复，区域银行更受贷款质量和融资成本影响。油价上升与长债收益率抬头，对银行净息差可能有利，信用成本也可能跟着上去。</p>
<h2 data-section-id="1bjy9yu" data-start="2711" data-end="2721">8. 风险预警</h2>
<p data-start="2723" data-end="2797">霍尔木兹现在是第一风险。伊朗说关闭，美国说开放，实际通航数据会决定油价。出现布雷、商船停航或保险公司停止承保，Brent冲破80美元的速度可能很快。</p>
<p data-start="2799" data-end="2891">AI交易集中度还在升。Nvidia一家公司对纳指和标普的拉动越来越大，Micron、Apple和部分软件已经多次掉队。TSMC或ASML只要给出一点低于预期的指引，半导体波动会被放大。</p>
<p data-start="2893" data-end="2954">美股盈利预期同比增长24%，容错空间不大。银行、半导体和大型科技都需要同时给出收入、利润和指引，单纯超过历史数字已经不够。</p>
<h2 data-section-id="1glety8" data-start="2956" data-end="2970">9. 今日重点关注事项</h2>
<p data-start="2972" data-end="3028">今天亚洲盘先看Brent、WTI、黄金、美元指数和美国股指期货。霍尔木兹实际船舶通行量，比双方表态更有交易价值。</p>
<p data-start="3030" data-end="3194">7月14日看美国CPI、JPMorgan和Goldman Sachs。7月15日看PPI、Bank of America、Citigroup、Wells Fargo及ASML。7月16日看零售销售、TSMC、Netflix和UnitedHealth。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 81px;"><a href="https://www.barrons.com/articles/inflation-bank-of-america-wells-fargo-goldman-asml-j-j-and-more-to-watch-this-week-71bddc40?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" alt="https://www.barrons.com/articles/inflation-bank-of-america-wells-fargo-goldman-asml-j-j-and-more-to-watch-this-week-71bddc40?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 81px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.barrons.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Barron's</span></span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+2</span></span><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute" style="opacity: 0; transform: translateX(10%);"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.jpmorganchase.com&amp;sz=128"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">JPMorgan Chase</span></span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+2</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<p data-start="3196" data-end="3206">三个深入思考的问题：</p>
<ol data-start="3208" data-end="3349">
<li data-section-id="1u7lcst" data-start="3208" data-end="3249">
<p data-start="3211" data-end="3249">霍尔木兹通航只下降一部分，油价会停在80美元附近，还是会因保险和运费先失控？</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="e61ccn" data-start="3251" data-end="3300">
<p data-start="3254" data-end="3300">TSMC和ASML继续上调AI需求时，市场会继续奖励扩产，还是开始计算2027年的产能过剩？</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17sx8oq" data-start="3302" data-end="3349">
<p data-start="3305" data-end="3349">银行财报如果交易收入强、贷款需求弱，美股会把它理解成金融市场繁荣，还是实体经济正在降温？</p>
</li>
</ol>
